org.apache.flex.compiler.ant.config

Class ConfigVariable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.ant.config.BaseConfigVariable
      • org.apache.flex.compiler.ant.config.ConfigVariable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOptionSource
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConfigBoolean, ConfigInt, ConfigString

    public abstract class ConfigVariable
extends BaseConfigVariable
    Provides a base class for Configuration Variables that can be set with a String value. Consumers of this class must implement the set isSet methods.
